:15.000Z","msg":"呢啲情況頭盔係好難解"},{"pid":"abd10c15aa00869ea812666c9e1c2c1f3703dc3e","tid":1585922,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:18:26.000Z","msg":"見到有手足除左佢頭盔<br />\n係第一步<br />\n之前就應該踢頭踢到佢暈<br />\n先<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可能</span>會放手"},{"pid":"34bd618fd64055539eb275fa2b1dcaccc922fe14","tid":1585922,"uid":98795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}